# Workspace: `dev-docs`

## Role

- **Developer-facing documentation** (build tooling, site config in `dev-docs/package.json`). Not part of the published editor bundle.

## Conventions

- Keep content accurate with the **current monorepo**; when documenting flows, reference real paths (`packages/excalidraw/...`, `excalidraw-app/...`).
- Follow whatever static-site or doc framework the folder already uses — do not introduce a second doc stack without an explicit decision.
- Typo/link fixes and clarifications are welcome; avoid stale claims about APIs that no longer exist.

## How to verify

- `yarn --cwd ./dev-docs typecheck`
- `yarn --cwd ./dev-docs build` (Docusaurus build must succeed)
- Optional: `yarn --cwd ./dev-docs start` and spot-check edited pages locally
